{"tid":225252,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"亞洲果種奴隸文化,幾時先改到?","createTime":"2017-05-01T15:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T18:13:37.000Z","uid":70760,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6371bec781df9ecba4cb3479308e256f38f079f6","tid":225252,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:56:09.000Z","msg":"有冇政治原因係入面?<br />\n<br />\n唔係支持或踩低咩國家, 此強彼弱, 歐美仲係強大, 亞洲平民應該都仲係繼續呢種生活"},{"pid":"d56fd21a0d48fd5678e85d1ad3eb8c5058228171","tid":225252,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:57:23.000Z","msg":"日本超越左好多歐洲國家啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5d0579446329db7a17dfb85accac2e5c0f0608","tid":225252,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:02:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本超越左好多歐洲國家啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔係好識, 有錯勿怪<br />\n<br />\n我既角度其實係工時同埋快樂指數出發<br />\n<br />\n如果你計國力或人均gdp, 日本的確都算前緣<br />\n<br />\n唔係支持中國, 中俄印度都係國力頭二,三, 同頭十內, 但你會唔會想係呢種地方生活  (之前係睇個咩調查講, 抱歉無source)"},{"pid":"8fed5d8141d063f76a5052749dfb998d0f66d75a","tid":225252,"uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:33:10.000Z","msg":"要屌就屌班頂爛市嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aba7de7b283e96152f7083a77bac3d842ec5d0e","tid":225252,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:36:26.000Z","msg":"帝制文化影響太耐"},{"pid":"165a20518cbc692b2fd390f58815a933de139bab","tid":225252,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:40:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7aaed177a4d9858207cfaff2891d0f5b4051879c","tid":225252,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:47:37.000Z","msg":"等人口跌下先啦<br />\n人口過剩 人力就自然唔值錢"},{"pid":"ab9dea1080c9718027eec7c933305902f6813bf2","tid":225252,"uid":13173,"like":0,"dislike":0,